.TH _ldapinit 1 "January 1, 2006"
.LO 1

.SH NAME
_ldapinit \- initializes the LDAP directory with a minimal tree.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B _ldapinit
.RB [[-h] | [-r | -s]]

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B [-h]
This help.
.TP
.B [-r]
Create only the root DN.
.TP
.B [-s]
Skip root DN creation (create only regular OUs).

.SH "SEE ALSO"
_lsldap(1), _ldapfinger(1), ldapscripts(5).

